{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f011f5a92b","title":"各兵团目前的工作方针","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"82cc10906c","index":0,"year":1936,"month":5,"day":5,"articleId":"f011f5a92b"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji8","name":"毛泽东全集第8卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji8.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji8":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"391f8c5c68","type":"paragraph","text":"各兵团目前的工作方针","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"f011f5a92b"},{"id":"ab86e20a21","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年5月5日）以十天为教育部队、总结经验及准备新行动的时间。各部队依照自己的情况，立即定出军事教育、政治教育、整理组织及总结在山西作战经验的具体办法。政治上解释与鼓动的基本口号：反对卖国蒋介石癌乱抗日后方，粉碎卖国贼对陕甘宁苏区的进攻，猛烈扩大抗日根据地硬甘苏区，争取迅速对日作战。在十天内由军委召集一次方面军以上干部大会，由军团及军召集一次庆祝胜利并追惊刘志丹同志大会。[1]","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"f011f5a92b"}],"page":{"id":"954d054a67","publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"f011f5a92b","start":404,"end":404}}}},"__N_SSG":true}